Class ValueEdge<A,L,W>

  • Object
    • ValueEdge<A,L,W>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - The type of the nodes' IDs
    L - The type of the nodes' label metadata
    W - The type of the weight metadata on the edge
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Edge<A,ValueNode<A,L>,ValueEdge<A,L,W>>, WeightedEdge<A,ValueNode<A,L>,W,ValueEdge<A,L,W>>

    public final class ValueEdge<A,L,W>
extends Object
implements WeightedEdge<A,ValueNode<A,L>,W,ValueEdge<A,L,W>>
    A WeightedEdge which is a value object, isomorphic to the two ValueNodes it connects and its weight.
